      "content": "thanks but the hotlines dont really do anything for the physical stuff. they just tell you to breathe or something... it doesn't change the fact that my nerves are literally on fire all the time. i feel like i'm trapped in a body that's just broken. it makes me think that maybe the only way to actually find peace is just to not exist anymore. does that sound crazy?",
